Defect ID

BUG-001

Defect Title

404 Error displayed when user clicks on Accessories category.

Module

Navigation Module

Severity

High

Priority

High

Environment
Application: Shoplane E-Commerce Website
Browser: Google Chrome
Operating System: Windows 10/11
Description

When the user clicks on the Accessories category from the navigation menu, the application redirects to a Page Not Found (404) screen instead of displaying the Accessories products.

Preconditions
User is on the Shoplane homepage.
Website is accessible.
Steps to Reproduce
Open Shoplane website.
Navigate to the top menu.
Click on "Accessories".
Observe the result.
Expected Result

Accessories products should be displayed on the page.

Actual Result

A 404 Page Not Found error page is displayed.

Status

Open

Attachment

404_Error.png

Recommendation

Verify the route mapping and product category navigation configuration for the Accessories page.